<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="grow-v">grow <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡrəʊ/    美 /ɡroʊ/  </p>
<p>(grew, grown)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi">1.★ <strong>vi 生长；成长：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Rice grows in warm climates.
水稻在温暖的气候下生长。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-vt">2.★ <strong>vt 种植；留 (须、发等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If I clear more land, I can grow more crops.
如果我开垦更多的土地，就能种更多的庄稼。</p><footer>2013 江西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>grow a beard / moustache
蓄胡须/胡子</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I've decided to <strong>grow</strong> my <strong>hair long</strong>.
我决定留长发。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-vi">3.★ <strong>vi 增长；增加：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My uncle hopes that his business will grow steadily.
我叔叔希望他的生意稳固发展。</p><footer>2016全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The population of this city is growing every year.
这个城市的人口每年都在增加。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[用作系动词] 逐渐变得；成为：</strong></h4>
<p>grow+adj：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Truth never grows old.
真理用不过时。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Another 15 minutes passed and I grew bored.
又过了15分钟，我开始变得不耐烦了。</p><footer>2017天津</footer></div>

<h4 id="5-vi">5.★ <strong>vi 逐渐形成；产生：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm sure you will <strong>grow to like</strong> her in time.
我肯定你慢慢就会喜欢她了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The best friendships are the ones that grow naturally.
自然形成的友谊才是最好的。</p><footer>2012辽宁</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="grow-into">grow into</h3>
<p>1.<strong>变成；发展成：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has grown into a fine young man.
他已长成一个不错的小伙子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The village where I was born has grown into a town.
我出生的那个村庄已经发展成为一个城镇。</p></div>

<h3 id="grow-out-of">grow out of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>产生于；长大得与…不再相称：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our friendship grew out of the experience of making that film.
我们的友谊源自于拍摄那部电影的经历。</p><footer>2017 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He's already grown out of his school uniform.
他已经长得穿不上校服了。</p></div>

<h3 id="grow-up">grow up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>成熟；长成；形成；发展：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Plants grow up towards the sunlight.
植物向阳生长。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The boy grew up (to be) a great scientist.
这个男孩长大后成了一名伟大的科学家。</p></div></div>